s investors would pay taxes every year on paper profits =E2=80=94 the rise =
in value of assets they still own =E2=80=94 even if they haven=E2=80=99t so=
ld anything.</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">This idea sparked a sharp sellof=
f in the Korean stock market today, with some already calling it =E2=80=9CB=
lack Tuesday.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">The Netherlands tried =
